Analysis by JLR and the supplier shows:  1. No fault with the hardware as the fault was in a different module or related to software  2. Pathfinder guided diagnostics were not used but would have helped to identify the correct repair  The Pathfinder guided diagnostics have been improved to include all known failure modes within the IMC and ISC plus the additional modules which make up the In-Control Touch Pro system.
